Machine learning models to prognose 30-Day Mortality in Postoperative 
Disseminated Cancer Patients.

Ganguli R(1), Franklin J(2), Yu X(3), Lin A(4), Lad R(5), Heffernan DS(6).

Author information:
(1)Brown University, USA.
